  "remarks": "TAi.013 Title: Mullah. Designation: Deputy Minister of Civil Aviation the Taliban regime. Member of the Taliban Military Commission as of mid-2013.  Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Barich tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 1 Jun. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended 3 September 2003, 9 July 2007, 21 Sep 2007, 13 Feb 2012, 13 Aug 2012, 22 April 2013 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
